skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: have you seen my
des: Have Alexa remember the stuff you stash or hide that you can never remember where you put it when you need it. Personal items, important documents, secret gifts - whatever the item is, simply tell her what it is and what location it will be in, and you can have her recall it for you any time in the future. You can store any number of objects and locations, update or remove things from your list, and find whatever you have stored in no time.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
